quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  31,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  31,2,yeh hikmat ki ( bhari hui ) kitaab ki ayatain hain
  31,3,naiko karon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  31,4,jo namaz ki pabandi karte aur zakaat dete aur akhirat ka yaqeen rakhtay hain
  31,5,yahi apne perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se hadaayat par hain aur yahi nijaat panay walay hain
  31,6,aur logon mein baaz aisa hai jo behooda hikaytein kharidata hai taakay ( logon ko ) be samjhay khuda ke raste se gumraah kere aur is seistehzaa kere yahi log hain jin ko zaleel karne wala azaab hoga
  31,7,aur jab is ko hamari ayatain sunai jati hain to akarr kar munh phair laita hai goya unn ko suna hi nahi jaisay unn ke kaanon mein saqal hai to is ko dard dainay walay azaab ki khushkhabri suna do
  31,8,jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay unn ke liye Nemat ke baagh hain
  31,9,hamesha unn mein rahen ge. khuda ka wada sacha hai aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  31,10,usi ne asmano ko satonon ke baghair pedakiya jaissa ke tum dekhte ho aur zameen par pahar ( bana kar ) rakh diye taakay tum ko hila hila nah day aur is mein har terhan ke janwar phela diye. aur hum hi ne asmano se pani nazilkiya phir ( uss se ) is mein har qisam ki nafees cheeze agayiN
  31,11,yeh to khuda ki paidaiesh hai to mujhe dikhao ke khuda ke siwa jo log hain onhon nekiya pedakiya hai? haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh zalim Sarih gumraahi mein hain
